<dl id="n03088g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n03" href="#n03088g">N03 (VI.B.3)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n03all.htm#n03088g"> 88(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">C</font> paralysed <font color="red"><sup><teeny>|a</teeny></sup></font>silver<font color="red"><sup><teeny>a|</teeny></sup></font> arm &amp; &mdash; / morbus pediculosus / wears Ardilaun&apos;s shirt </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: See also: <a name="n03087f" href="n03all.htm#n03087f">N03 (VI.B.3):087(f)</a>. <i>Morbus pediculosus</i>: an ancient disease in which the body swarmed with lice. See <cite>Ulysses</cite> 5.306f, &ldquo;lord Ardilaun has to change his shirt four times a day, they say. Skin breeds lice or vermin.&rdquo;.</mm> </dd></dl>
